 Sender name.  Will you test a female name against a male name? Or perhaps a company name against an individual? 
 Subject line.  Will you highlight one particular article in your newsletter? Or maybe focus on a percentage discount for one of your products? 
 
 Split testing is the best way to guarantee relevant and targeted content to audience segments, and ultimately, better engagement with them. 
