 Why assign values?  The way users make purchasing decisions is not always straightforward, and they may arrive at conversions by many different means! As such, it's important to understand the role each channel plays, as seen in  Figure 9.40 , so that a given channel can be optimized properly and any expenditure justified. 
 
 
